    <tags>opencomic comics comic webtoon manga image images reader viewer book ebook epub cbr cbz cb7 jpeg png gif webp</tags>
    <summary>Comic and Manga reader</summary>
    <description>
      Comic and Manga reader

      ## Features
      - 🖼 Support this image formats: `JPG`, `PNG`, `APNG`, `AVIF`, `WEBP`, `GIF`, `SVG`, `BMP`, `ICO`
      - 🗄 Support this compressed formats: `RAR`, `ZIP`, `7Z`, `TAR`, `CBR`, `CBZ`, `CB7`, `CBT`
      - 📄 Support this documents/ebook formats: `PDF`, `EPUB` (Alpha)
      - 🎵 Support background music from folder: `MP3`, `M4A`, `WEBM`, `WEBA`, `OGG`, `OPUS`, `WAV`, `FLAC`
      - 📁 Master folders support
      - ☁️ Server connection support: `smb://`, `ftp://`, `ftps://`, `scp://`, `sftp://`, `ssh://`
      - 🇯🇵 Manga read mode
      - 🇰🇷 Webtoon read mode
      - 📖 Double page view
      - 🔖 Bookmarks and continue reading
      - 🔍 Floating magnifying glass
      - 🖱 Reading in scroll or slide
      - ⚪ Adjust the brightness, saturation, contrast, sepia, negative and invert colors
      - 🎨 Colorize black and white images
      - 🔄 Tracking with sites (AniList)
      - 🎮 Gamepad navigation
      - 🔢 Multiple interpolation methods: `lanczos3`, `lanczos2`, `mitchell`, `cubic`, `nearest` and others
     </description>
    <releaseNotes>
      ##### 🚀 New Features

      - Delete bookmarks from the bookmark list
      - Save and show also the current folder progress apart from the main folder
      - Instead of the file name it shows the title of EPUB, PDF and Compressed Files with ComicInfo.xml

      ##### 🐛 Bug Fixes

      - Error when resizing after exit comic opened from recents
      - When reloading, change view or sorting a folder opens reading mode in some cases
      - Reading shortcuts remain active when going back to recently opened
      - Some errors on go back before comic load
      - Blank page keep white color in dark theme
      - Open with OpenComic not working in macOS and some fixes in Windows and Linux
      - Error opening an epub when OpenComic is closed
      - Performance issues when generating some thumbnails
    </releaseNotes>
  </metadata>
  <files>
    <!-- this section controls what actually gets packaged into the Chocolatey package -->
    <file src="tools\**" target="tools" />
  </files>
</package>
